/06/re-read-tyrion-i-wounds-of-betrayal.html\">Analyses and summary of the chapter</a> in the course of a 10th reread by Slynth.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/09/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-3\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords part 3</a> Analyses and summary by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404075434\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.097 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.463 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 265/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1242/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8969/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1501/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.240/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  432.151      1 -total\n 99.20%  428.704      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 98.92%  427.496      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 98.62%  426.172      1 Template:Infobox\n  1.16%    5.017      2 Template:Work_color\n  0.36%    1.555      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    1.470      2 Template:Columns\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:6044-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404075433 and revision id 241674\n -->\n",
